{
  "stem": "26672.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's been here several time--he actually came with me to England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he left for Australia he had two uncles that survived the war and took him over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They went after the war to Australia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they took him, and brought him to Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Unfortunately, when I went this time-- I remember that his uncles from the camps, early camp days-- and they weren't alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was very sorry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One dies within weeks before I got there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was rather upset.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I thought they might have been able to tell me about my father, because they were much older, and they knew my father.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came another one that came across, much younger [INAUDIBLE] my age, who said to me, he remembered me from home and he met my father.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what he look like?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, like all Jews with a beard and a certain type cap.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know it didn't help very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German army.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, uh, when the planes came over, and after they-- it-- it-- it died down a bit, we, um, his children-- my parents took me away to another town called [?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jelehova. ?] And-- and there we've spent a few months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came back German occupation [INAUDIBLE] and it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father carried on business with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember one year the army provided them with an escort and a lorry to go to Lublin, to bring back flour for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When exactly it was I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But so we must have carried them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He must have had some-- some-- made some friends in the German occupation now, because I have a telegram which was sent via that person.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
